text: Daphnella sinuata is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Raphitomidae.Gastropods.com: Daphnella sinuata ==Description== The length of the shell attains 11 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Pacific Panama ==References== ==External links== * sinuata Category:Gastropods described in 1856
title: Daphnella sinuata
